# Design System

## Component Colors (exact hex)

| Widget | Color |
|--------|-------|
| CPU | `#ff2d95` |
| RAM | `#00d4ff` |
| GPU | `#9d4edd` |
| Network | `#00fff7` |
| DNS & Latence Jeu | `#00ff9d` |

## 8px Grid

Margins, paddings, gaps, sizes = multiples of 8px (4px only for fine details).

- Tight coupling (icon+label): `gap-2` (8px)
- Section separation: `space-y-6` / `gap-6` (24px)

## Border Radius

- Main bento cards: `rounded-[2rem]` (32px)
- Inner panels: `rounded-2xl` (16px)
- Buttons/inputs/tabs: `rounded-xl` (12px) or `rounded-lg` (8px)

## Theme Tokens (`globals.css`)

Use CSS variables — never hardcode `slate-*` for surfaces:

- `--surface-inset`, `--surface-muted`, `--surface-raised` — panels and rows
- `--text-muted`, `--text-subtle` — secondary text (WCAG AAA)
- `--overlay` — modal backdrops
- `--border`, `--border-strong`

**Glassmorphism (`html:not(.no-blur)`):**
- `bento-card::before` grain **disabled** — grain + translucency + blur = ugly texture
- Zen dark: `[data-zen-mode="true"] .bento-card` — `color-mix(card-solid 88%)`, blur 12 px

**Light mode (`[data-theme="light"]`):** palette **Daylight Neon** — canvas `#e4e8f2`, néons de marque conservés, glows via `getNeonTextShadow(color, isDark)` in `src/utils/neonEffects.ts`. CPU equalizer trough: `--spectrum-trough`.

## Accessibility

- WCAG AAA contrast (≥ 7:1) for metrics text
- Full ARIA structure, keyboard navigation
- Escape closes modals, **gaming latency detail panel**, and exits Zen Mode
- **Global** toast: `StatusToast` — `role="status"` + `aria-live="polite"` (DNS/pilotes/télémétrie)
- Settings modal toasts: footer slot, same ARIA pattern
- Settings Reset: double-confirmation state

## Zen Mode

- Load state: `Math.max(cpuUsage, gpuUsage)` — exclude passive RAM cache
- Unmount heavy SVG charts and dashboard widgets when Zen Mode is active
- **SakuraParticles** stay mounted — en Zen : intensité **faible ou moyen** selon réglage (`high` plafonné à `medium`), **pas de couche front** (gros pétales)
- **`data-zen-mode="true"`** on `<html>` when Zen active (`App.tsx`)
- **Glass sombre + Zen:** grain SVG off on glass cards; zen bento panel 88 % opaque, blur 12 px (`globals.css`)
- **StatsBar hidden** — telemetry inside `ZenClockWidget` card (`TelemetryGrid variant="embedded"`)
- Gaming latency panel (badge Jeu) works same as dashboard
- Antivirus badge below telemetry: `Protégé · {product_name}` from real WMI detection
- Card width: `max-w-[min(100%,64rem)]` for fullscreen-friendly layout

## Brand — SlashTitle

- Core: `SlashTitle.tsx` — katana SVG drops, cyan flash, text splits into « Koi » / « Monitor »
- Sizes: `lg` splash, `md` settings About tab, `sm` title bar
- `SplashSlashTitle.tsx` wraps `lg`
- CSS in `globals.css`: `.splash-title-gradient`, `.splash-aurora`, progress shimmer keyframes
- `prefers-reduced-motion`: skip katana motion, instant or shortened split
- TitleBar: `playSlashAnimation={!showSplash}` in `App.tsx`; About tab replays via `aboutSlashKey`
